ZH: 我对花粉过敏。
EN: I am allergic to pollen.

ZH: 小猫对鱼过敏。
EN: The kitten is allergic to fish.

ZH: 他对坚果过敏。
EN: He is allergic to nuts.

ZH: 她对药物过敏。
EN: She is allergic to medication.

ZH: 孩子对牛奶过敏。
EN: The child is allergic to milk.

ZH: 我对尘螨过敏。
EN: I am allergic to dust mites.

ZH: 你对香水过敏吗？
EN: Are you allergic to perfumes?

ZH: 跟我一起吃饭的人对海鲜过敏。
EN: The person I was dining with is allergic to seafood.

ZH: 他对酒精过敏。
EN: He is allergic to alcohol.

ZH: 她对花生过敏。
EN: She is allergic to peanuts.

ZH: 我对猫过敏，所以我们家里不能养猫。
EN: I am allergic to cats, so we cannot have a cat in our house.

ZH: 这位女士对花粉过敏，所以春天她总是打喷嚏。
EN: The lady is allergic to pollen, so she always sneezes in the spring.

ZH: 小明对蛋过敏，不能吃蛋糕。
EN: Xiaoming is allergic to eggs, so he cannot eat cake.

ZH: 我对刺激性气味过敏。
EN: I am allergic to strong smells.

ZH: 他对大豆过敏。
EN: He is allergic to soybeans.

ZH: 她对香菇过敏。
EN: She is allergic to mushrooms.

ZH: 我对虾过敏。
EN: I am allergic to shrimp.

ZH: 你对花过敏吗？
EN: Are you allergic to flowers?

ZH: 她对草过敏，每次出去都得戴口罩。
EN: She is allergic to grass, so she has to wear a mask every time she goes out.

ZH: 在这个季节，我对花粉过敏。
EN: I am allergic to pollen during this season.
